customer_reviews.title: My son loves this particular model of UA Football cleats for Football & lax; requested exact replacement for this year.

product_meta.title: Under Armour Men's UA Highlight MC Lacrosse Cleats
product_meta.description: Bring the opposing team to its knees in the Under Armour UA Highlight MC football cleat. UA ClutchFit upper wraps your foot in a “second skin” of advantages for powerful support & an incredible feel. Lightweight material innovation forms to the contours of your foot, amping your joints & muscles to give you better feel, fit & support. Weight: 11.2 oz.
feature_bullets: UA ClutchFit Upper Wraps your Foot in a “Second Skin” of Advantages for Powerful Support & an Incredible Feel
Extended Eyerow Cut-Outs for Better Ease of Entry & Superior Flexibility
Molded 4D Foam Footbed Conforms to your Foot's Exact Shape, Eliminating Slippage & Reducing Cleat Pressure
UA PlasmaX Plate Powers your Foot's Natural Motion for Maximum Traction & Stability
V56 Technology in the Forefoot is Engineered to Help Limit Toe Hyperextension
